 ('109', 'field', '57', 'en_ie', ' salesforce is the world s leading crm software and enterprise cloud ecosystem their customer success platform helps businesses grow into a more streamlined effective and efficient organisations across sales service marketing and more the sonica ops team has had the pleasure of being part of sfdc s expansion by servicing their ever increasing head count and office space requirements for the past 3 years it is therefore with great pride that we showcase the latest sfdc office completion a 15 000 sq ft floor plate in central park works involved the demolition and strip out of the previous tenant s existing fitted offices to cater for the new salesforce remodelled floor plate layout the office design placed emphasis on increased team collaboration with all new open plan workstations meeting rooms offices boardrooms flexible spaces staff kitchens canteen areas breakout areas and a number of bespoke techforce bars all part of the required brief they have since been voted ireland s best workplace the company was ranked no 1 on the list of the best large places to work a ranking based on employees own assessments of their experiences '),
